6 Section 1-9-102. A. 1. In coordination with the Oklahoma
7 Commission on Children and Youth, each district attorney shall
8 develop a multidisciplinary child abuse team in each county of the
9 district attorney or in a contiguous group of counties.
10 2. The lead agency for the team shall be chosen by the members
11 of the team. The team shall intervene in reports review cases
